body.name: YITAHOME 5 Tiers Bookshelf, Classically Modern White Bookshelf, Book Rack, Storage Rack Shelves in Living Room/Home/Office, Books Holder Organizer for Books/Movies, White
features: ARTSY MODERN DESIGN- Streamlined minimalism meets modern in this chic bookcase. Its elegant look and simple structure makes it a fashionable and functional fit in any room.

VERSATILE OPEN 5 SHELVES- Open shelves and stable structure provide enough storage space, allowing you to show off your displays in every direction. Perfect for organizing books, family photos, potted plants, CDs, ornaments, and more.

DURABLE & STURDY- Crafted with wrought iron in a matte black finish, and constructed from sturdy boards and black coated metal frame. Uniquely designed metal sidebars with X-shaped rod in the back provides constant stability.

ANTI-TIP KITS & EASY ASSEMBLY- Please remember to install the anti-tilting tool on the wall for better stability and less unexpected injuries. All necessary accessories, tools, and illustrated instruction will be packed. You can finish the whole installation effortlessly and quickly.

MULTI-ZONE STORAGE- This functional bookshelf takes up limited space. Can meet your storage needs as it not only acts as a bookshelf, but also is a great plant shelf or display shelf in your living room, bedroom, study, entrance, hallway, office, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Strong and beautiful.
reviews.reviewText: Great deal for the money and easy to assemble. I changed my desk, but my new desk did not have a credenza or shelves, so I needed to purchase this shelf. It was sized perfectly for the space I had, and it looks great! Strong and sturdy, and I love the black & white!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: This is a very nice piece of furniture. It was easy to assemble and works great for the space I wanted it for. I have no regrets about getting it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for the price.
reviews.reviewText: Bought two of these as "throw away furniture" pieces as inexpensive options for a temporary office space. They are great for the price and are quite sturdy and look good unlike some really cheap ones you can find. Very easy to assemble with everything you need in the kit unless you need to secure them to the wall, then you will need your own drill. Nothing "fancy" but will do the job if you are looking for something inexpensive, yet nice looking.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy & look good!
reviews.reviewText: The shelves arrived very quickly. They were great quality and went together easily. We ordered 2 and would order more if needed.Good value for the quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Gorgeous and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: The finished assembled piece is gorgeous. It looks exactly as pictured (I got the black metal with white shelves) and it’s beautiful. The shelves seem to be good quality. I was impressed by the look of them.Everything arrived safely with no damage. The unit was packed well with plenty of styrofoam and all pieces were bagged individually to prevent scuffing, etc.The instructions were great. The pictures and written directions were clear and easy to follow. The only snafu I had during assembly was one screw had a defect that wouldn’t allow the hex wrench to sit properly in it and turn it so it was unusable. Thankfully there was an extra screw included so it wasn’t an issue.At one point early on, when I was assembling the side rail pieces (step one), the top and bottom parts of the rails didn’t seem to sit flush together and I wondered if this would cause a misalignment with the holes and screws but it did not. The top part of the railing didn’t fit snugly/sit flush over the bottom part on both the left and right sides but it was a non-issue. The screw had no problem entering the hole that kept the two pieces together.I’m impressed and very happy with my purchase! The whole unit is sturdy and the shelves feel strong. Quick and easy to put together. Highly recommend this one!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Study and great height!
reviews.reviewText: Recently moved into a new home and wanted to display my sentimental items. I bought the 5 tier shelve. It was very easy to put together and holds up with my two cats climbing on the shelves. It has a beautiful modern look. Highly recommend for an affordable display for your space!
